data.title: Do native English speakers find it weird when foreigners speak fluent English?
data.meta_description:
Answer (1 of 3): I have met hundreds, if not thousands of non-native speakers who speak excellent English, but you could always realise that they were not native, there was always that small mistake, that little pronunciation error that gave it away.
